 318, \"to\": 335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS Published\\u00c2Apr 17, 2024, 10:40 PM Updated\\u00c2Apr 18, 2024, 10:56 PM LONDON\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093London Marathon event director Hugh Brasher is predicting a more competitive women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s race on April 21 than the 2024 Paris Olympic marathon later in the summer, and believes the women-only world record may fall.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brasher,_New_York\", \"score\": 0.9691301660371875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brasher\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brasher,_New_York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brasher,_New_York\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 361}, {\"ngram\": \"10:40 PM\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"a more competitive women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s race\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympic marathon\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"the women-only world record\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s fastest female marathoner Tigst Assefa headlines an elite field that features 10 women who have run under 2hr 17min 30sec, including three of the top-four fastest women ever.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s fastest female marathoner Tigst Assefa\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite field\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"10 women\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"2hr 17min 30sec\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"the top-four fastest women\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNo race in the history of our sport has ever had that,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Brasher said on April 17. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo I have no idea who\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to win but I think it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to be an incredibly competitive event.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 912, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brasher,_New_York\", \"score\": 0.9691301660371875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brasher\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brasher,_New_York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brasher,_New_York\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNo race\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredibly competitive event\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be a harder marathon to win than the Olympic Marathon in Paris, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m pretty certain of that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Assefa clocked 2:11:53 at the Berlin Marathon in September, setting the world record for women in a race alongside men runners, and is aiming to break Mary Keitany\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s mark of 2:17:01 set in a women-only race at the 2017 London Marathon.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998540261, \"rank\": 1.4599704883082632e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"score\": 0.6116152531455707, \"rank\": 0.5495111053212951, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q7